{
  "stem": "8895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then when-- later on, one of my teachers wore an SS uniform, SS uniform, into a class.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Came in-- and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a very religious school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The teacher would come into the class, and he would say, 'blessed is the Lord,' and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The children had to say, 'forever and ever, amen.' And in the corner stood the statue of Maria.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they had to ask, what would you rather say, this or 'Heil Hitler'?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Would you believe that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, 'Heil Hitler.' I never-- I never put my hand up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in this school, it was OK, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why did you move schools?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very good, because the Catholic school was the best.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- you can't-- you could only-- they could only have a certain percentage of Jewish people in each school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was non-Aryan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I went there before, because we went away so early on from Germany-- '33.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, not very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what I was considered in the Catholic school, but I certainly hadn't-- didn't have any religious-- The Catholics were very, very firm, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very, very.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I experienced once anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the children learned that and they came back from their religious class and went to the Jewish children, and said, you-- you-- you killed Christ.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the only thing I can remember, the only one thing I can remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't-- you couldn't miss it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could not miss it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were always in the [INAUDIBLE], and so they had to stand like that, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Horrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
